---
import Breadcrumb from "../../components/Breadcrumb.astro";
import DonationCard from "../../components/DonationCard.astro";
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { SEO } from "astro-seo";
const title = "Pay for Cooked Food Appeal | Feed the Hunger | CRF ";
const description =
  "Donate to Care and relief foundation Cooked Food Appeal to provide hot meals to low income families & children who lost their parents. Act Now";
const keywords =
  "Cooked Food,cooked food donation,cooked meal,feed the hungry,hot meal donation";
const pageImage = "";
---

<SEO
  title={title}
  description={description}
  canonical=""
  openGraph={{
    basic: {
      title: `${title}`,
      type: "website",
      image: `${pageImage? pageImage : "/assets/images/logo/Logo-CRF.png"}`,
    },
    optional: {
      description: `${description}`,
    },
  }}
  twitter={{
    creator: "@jonasmerlins1",
  }}
  extend={{
    // extending the default link tags
    link: [{ rel: "icon", href: "/favicon.png" }],
    // extending the default meta tags
    meta: [
      {
        name: "twitter:image",
        content: `${pageImage ? pageImage : "/assets/images/logo/Logo-CRF.png"}`,
      },
      {
        name: "twitter:title",
        content: `${title}`,
      },
      {
        name: "twitter:description",
        content: `${description}`,
      },
      { name: "keywords", content: `${keywords}` },
    ],
  }}
/>
<Layout>
  <main>
    <Breadcrumb
      title="Cooked Food Appeal"
      link="/assets/images/appeals/masjid-4.png"
      image="/assets/images/breadcrumb-bg.jpg"
    />
    <DonationCard
      programId={[65,66,67,68]}
      title="CRF Cooked Food Appeal"
      description="Food Donation"
      style="col-xl-3 col-lg-3 col-md-6 col-sm-12"
    />

    <section class="section-padding">
      <div class="container mt-5">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="row justify-content-between align-items-center">
            <!-- First Div: Image -->
            <div class="col-12 col-md-5 mb-4 mb-md-0">
              <img
                src="/assets/images/appeals/masjid-4.png"
                alt="Rounded Image"
                class="img-fluid rounded"
              />
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-7 mb-4 align-self-center">
              <div class="section-tittle mb-35">
                <span class="sub-tittle text-capitalize font-600"
                  >Our Impact</span
                >
                <h2 class="title font-700 pb-15">
                  Distribute Hot Meals to Those Who Need It
                </h2>
                <p class="pera-subtitle mb-15">
                  Food insecurity in the UK has escalated, leaving countless
                  families in distress due to severe flooding and disrupted food
                  supply chains. Over 2+ million children are now facing hunger,
                  and for many low-income households, a single hot meal has
                  becomev a rare comfort. Initiatives like <span
                    style="font-weight: 600;">food donation</span
                  > are now more crucial than ever to support those struggling to
                  access basic necessities.
                  <br /><br />
                  Your support can make a difference. By donating our Care and Relief
                  Foundation <span style="font-weight: 600;"
                    >cooked food appeal</span
                  >, you can provide hot meals to vulnerable families & the
                  children who lost their parents, easing their hunger and
                  offering them the Nutrition they need to survive.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="col-lg-10 mt-10">
                <a
                  href="https://crf-donate.tscube.co.in/"
                  class="btn btn-primary-fill"
                  >Donate Now
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Second Div: Heading and Paragraph -->
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="blog-details top-bottom-padding2">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row gy-24">
          <div class="">
            <div class="single-blog">
              <div class="blog-img">
                <div>
                  <div class="video-section">
                    <iframe
                      width="100%"
                      height="600px"
                      id="video"
                      src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/w7NuL2e3KiE?si=cBLdztiMqnAQMat9"
                      frameborder="0"
                      allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
                      allowfullscreen></iframe>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="blog-info">
                <div class="blog-info-title">
                  <div class="flex gap-16 mb-20 align-items-center"></div>
                  <h4 class="title">Feed the Hunger</h4>
                  <p class="subtitle">
                    A simple act does not affect you entire life, but it bring
                    relief and hope in the life they face most challenging
                    moments. Feed the hunger is not only a charitable act but a
                    way to earn massive spiritual reward. By donating your
                    Sadaqah through care and relief foundation cooked food
                    appeal, you can bring new hope to the families who need it
                    the most.
                  </p>
                  <div class="divider"></div>

                  <!-- <p class="subtitle">
                    In addition to these benefits, contributing to charity
                    through Sadaqah also plays a crucial role in fostering a
                    sense of unity and community. The act of giving, rooted in
                    the principles of generosity and compassion, not only
                    positively impacts individuals in need but also strengthens
                    the bond among members of society.
                  </p> -->
                  <div class="divider"></div>
                  <div class="quote-with-text">
                    <div class="quote">
                      <svg
                        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                        width="76"
                        height="54"
                        viewBox="0 0 76 54"
                        fill="none"
                      >
                        <path
                          d="M67.1429 32.4V30.4H65.1429H54.2857C49.3919 30.4 45.4286 26.4424 45.4286 21.6V10.8C45.4286 5.95763 49.3919 2 54.2857 2H65.1429C70.0366 2 74 5.95763 74 10.8V16.2V21.6V33.75C74 43.8236 65.7956 52 55.6429 52H54.2857C52.3776 52 50.8571 50.4724 50.8571 48.6C50.8571 46.7276 52.3776 45.2 54.2857 45.2H55.6429C61.9794 45.2 67.1429 40.0789 67.1429 33.75V32.4ZM23.7143 32.4V30.4H21.7143H10.8571C5.96336 30.4 2 26.4424 2 21.6V10.8C2 5.95763 5.96336 2 10.8571 2H21.7143C26.6081 2 30.5714 5.95763 30.5714 10.8V16.2V21.6V33.75C30.5714 43.8236 22.367 52 12.2143 52H10.8571C8.94907 52 7.42857 50.4724 7.42857 48.6C7.42857 46.7276 8.94907 45.2 10.8571 45.2H12.2143C18.5509 45.2 23.7143 40.0789 23.7143 33.75V32.4Z"
                          stroke="#090E0D"
                          stroke-width="4"></path>
                      </svg>
                    </div>
                    <!-- <h4 class="title">
                      Prophet (PBUH) saying: “Whoever builds a masjid for the
                      sake of Allah, Allah will build for him a house in
                      Paradise.”
                    </h4> -->
                  </div>
                  <div class="d-flex gap-20">
                    <div class="blog-multi-img">
                      <img
                        src="/assets/images/appeals/masjid-1.png"
                        alt="image"
                      />
                    </div>
                    <div class="blog-multi-img">
                      <img
                        src="/assets/images/appeals/masjid-2.png"
                        alt="image"
                      />
                    </div>
                    <div class="blog-multi-img">
                      <img
                        src="/assets/images/appeals/masjid-3.png"
                        alt="image"
                      />
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="donation-content">
                    <h4 class="title">
                      Why Donate to CRF's Cooked Food Project?
                    </h4>
                    <p class="pera">
                      Our cooked food donation programme focuses on the most
                      needy communities, especially in remote areas where access
                      to food services is very less. Through your donation, we
                      can deliver hot cooked meal to those who is in struggle,
                      prioritizing widows, orphans, and families.
                      <br /><br />By supporting care and relief foundation
                      cooked food donation programme, you are not just offering
                      hot cooked meal & hope but also you are offering greatly
                      improving their health and overall well-being.
                    </p>
                    <ul class="bullet-list">
                      <li class="list">
                        <span style="font-weight: 700;">Improve Health: </span>
                        Your donation provides nutritious meals that help combat
                        malnutrition, improving the health and well-being of vulnerable
                        individuals, especially children and the elderly.
                      </li>
                      <li class="list">
                        <span style="font-weight: 700;"
                          >Hope and Dignity:
                        </span>
                        By providing a hot meal, your support restores dignity to
                        those suffering from hunger, giving them hope during difficult
                        times of hardship.
                      </li>
                      <li class="list">
                        <span style="font-weight: 700;"
                          >Nutritional Support :</span
                        >
                        Each meal offers essential nutrients, ensuring families receive
                        balanced, healthy food that supports physical strength and
                        daily energy levels for survival.
                      </li>
                      <li class="list">
                        <span style="font-weight: 700;"
                          >Protection from begging :</span
                        >
                        Your contribution prevents families from resorting to begging,
                        reducing their vulnerability to exploitation and providing
                        them with the basic food they deserve.
                      </li>
                    </ul>

                    <div class="divider"></div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="donation-content">
                    <h4 class="title">
                      Ways to Donate for the Cooked Food Appeal
                    </h4>
                    <p class="pera">
                      Your support is vital in providing nourishment to those in
                      need. Here are the different ways you can donate and make
                      a meaningful difference:
                    </p>
                    <ul class="bullet-list">
                      <li class="list">
                        <span style="font-weight: 700;"
                          >1- One-Time Donation:
                        </span>
                        A one-time donation ensures that individuals and families
                        in need receive a hot, nutritious meal when they need it
                        the most. Every contribution matters.
                      </li>
                      <li class="list">
                        <span style="font-weight: 700;"
                          >2- Online Donations:
                        </span>
                        Donate easily and securely through our online platform. Whether
                        it's a one-time or recurring donation, your online contribution
                        helps provide immediate relief to those in need.
                      </li>
                      <li class="list">
                        <span style="font-weight: 700;"
                          >3- Monthly Contribution:
                        </span>
                        By committing to a monthly donation, you can help provide
                        continuous support, ensuring that no one goes without food.
                        Your ongoing support brings hope every day.
                      </li>
                      <li class="list">
                        <span style="font-weight: 700;"
                          >4- Zakat Donations :</span
                        >
                        Fulfill your Zakat obligation by donating to the Cooked Food
                        Appeal. Your contribution helps feed the most vulnerable,
                        improving their health and quality of life.
                      </li>
                      <li class="list">
                        <span style="font-weight: 700;"
                          >5- Sadaqah Giving :</span
                        >
                        Give Sadaqah to provide essential meals to those suffering
                        from hunger. Your act of charity brings both physical relief
                        and spiritual rewards.
                      </li>
                      <li class="list">
                        <span style="font-weight: 700;"
                          >6- Corporate Donations :</span
                        >
                        Partner with CRF as a corporate sponsor. Your company's donation
                        can feed hundreds of families and make a lasting difference
                        in the lives of those struggling with hunger).
                      </li>
                    </ul>
                    <div class="divider"></div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="donation-content">
                    <h4 class="title">
                      What Qur'an Says? About Those Who Feed Others
                    </h4>
                    <p class="pera">
                      <span style="font-size: larger;">
                        “Give food, out of love for Him, to the poor and the
                        orphan and the captive, [saying] “We feed you, for
                        Allah’s pleasure only — We desire from you neither
                        reward nor thanks.” (Holy Qur’an 76:5-12).</span
                      >

                      <br /><br />
                      Since 2016, Care and Relief Foundation has been dedicated to
                      providing freshly cooked meals to thousands of individuals
                      and families across the UK and beyond. With a strong network
                      of local teams, supply chains, and deep knowledge of the communities
                      we serve, we are able to reach even the most remote areas where
                      hunger is most critical. <br /><br />
                      Our food-related campaigns are dedicated to Tackling the severe
                      hunger crisis affecting millions of families in the UK, where
                      poverty and malnutrition continue to destroy lives. Thanks
                      to your generous cooked food donations, including Sadaqah and
                      Zakat, we've been able to bring immediate relief to those are
                      suffering. By providing nourishing cooked meals, we are feeding
                      the weak, weary, and malnourished, bringing hope and restoring
                      dignity to those who need it most. <br /><br />
                      Care and Relief Foundation's Feed the Hungry program is providing
                      essential, nutritious meals to thousands of people, alleviating
                      food insecurity and improving their quality of life. Your donations
                      whether in the form of Sadaqah or Zakat directly support this
                      initiative. Every contribution ensures that cooked meals reach
                      those most in need, making a significant difference in their
                      lives and health.
                    </p>

                    <div class="divider"></div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <!-- blog info -->
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <style>
        @media screen and (max-width: 768px) {
          #video {
            height: 300px;
          }
        }
      </style>
    </section>
    <!-- Faq section started -->
    <section class="question-area section-padding">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col my-auto">
            <!-- Section Tittle -->
            <div class="section-tittle mb-50" style="text-align: center;">
              <h2 class="title font-700">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
              <p class="pera">
                When deciding which charity to donate to, it's important to do
                your search and find one that aligns with your values and
                interests.
              </p>
            </div>
